snippet.title: 6/10/19 Child Abduction Emergency (AMBER ALERT) League City, Texas NOAA Weather Radio
snippet.description:
BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DIVISION OF EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT
RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE SAN ANGELO TX
743 PM CDT MON JUN 10 2019

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DIVISION OF EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT.

THE LEAGUE CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR MALAKHI ELIJAH
BANKHEAD, A BLACK MALE, 2 YEARS OLD, DATE OF BIRTH, JULY 1 2016,
HEIGHT 3 FEET 2 INCHES, WEIGHT 35 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR, BROWN EYES.
HAS ECZEMA ON HIS ELBOW.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR KATHERINE NICOLE ULRICH, A WHITE, FEMALE, 21
YEARS OLD, DATE OF BIRTH JULY 18, 1997, HEIGHT 5 FEET 11 INCHES,
WEIGHT 150 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, BROWN EYES AND HAS NUMEROUS TATTOOS,
IN CONNECTION WITH HIS ABDUCTION.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR CODY ALBERT BANKHEAD, BLACK, MALE, 24 YEARS
OLD, DATE OF BIRTH JANUARY 20, 1995, HEIGHT 5 FEET 10 INCHES, WEIGHT
160 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR, BROWN EYES AND HAS A SCAR ON HIS UPPER ARM,
IN CONNECTION WITH HIS ABDUCTION.

THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A WHITE, 2015, BMW X3 WITH A TEXAS, LICENSE
PLATE NUMBER OF K S W 8 6 5 6.

THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN LEAGUE CITY, TEXAS.

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER.

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE LEAGUE
CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 281-332-2566.

NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS LEAGUE CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT AT
281-554-1844.
